# Smart Ticket Management (SERVICE CRM)

## Implemented
- `ticket_number` + `#TK-xxxxx` display and search
- `body_cleaned` + `message-filter.ts` for LLM
- Batch reclassify: `POST /api/tickets/reclassify/batch` + **SSE** `GET .../batch/[jobId]/stream`
- Multi-agent: `POST /api/ai/agent` + `AiAgentPanel` on dashboard
- Virtual list: `VirtualTicketList` + `@tanstack/react-virtual`
- Mobile-first: `crm-touch-target`, `crm-mobile-bottom-bar`, `BatchProgressBar`

## Secrets
- Gmail OAuth vars in environment only — never commit tokens to `src/`.

## After deploy
Run `POST /api/init` once for schema (`ticket_number`, `body_cleaned`, `ai_batch_jobs.payload`).
